            </div>

            <section class="descripcion__producto"> 
                <h3>Descripción</h3>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sit, fugiat.</li>
                            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.</li>
                            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Minus porro 
                                ducimus ipsa!</li>
                            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. 
                                Ea dolorum excepturi velit.</li>
